        "question": "<p><span style=\"font-family:'Cambria Math'\">The New Moore Island is in geographic proximity to:</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;line-height:115%;font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Cambria Math'\">SSC CGL 25/09/2024 (2nd Shift)</span></p>",
