n style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">.</span></li> <li><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">It lay near the </span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">Sundarbans delta</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">, which spans southern Bangladesh and West Bengal (India).</span></li> <li><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">No permanent settlement</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Cambria Math'\"> ever existed on the island.</span></li> </ul>"
