><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">One of the highest passes in the world used historically for trade.</span></li><li><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">Zojila Pass</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Cambria Math'\"> connects Srinagar to Leh, but </span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">not to China</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">.</span></li></ul>"
