ly:'Cambria Math'\">Name means “White Peak of the Three Spiritual Brothers.”</span></li><li><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">It remains a symbol of Bhutan’s </span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">religious and natural heritage</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Cambria Math'\">.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;line-height:115%;font-size:12pt\"></p>"
